# Design Direction

Primary inspiration:

- https://www.second-shopper.com/
- https://recraft.ai/

Do NOT copy layouts.

Instead capture the feeling.

## Visual Style

The design should feel:

- Soft
- Warm
- Spacious
- Editorial
- Premium
- Calm

## Colors

Use warm natural colors.

Backgrounds should never be pure white.

Preferred palette:

- Background
- Warm Cream
- Sand
- Olive
- Warm Brown
- Dark Charcoal

Accent colors should be used sparingly.

## Typography

Typography is extremely important.

Inspired by Second Shopper.

Characteristics:

- Very large hero headings
- Tight line-height
- Strong visual hierarchy
- Lots of whitespace
- Clean editorial feeling

Never use tiny headings.

## Spacing

Prefer generous spacing.

Large vertical padding.

Avoid crowded layouts.

## Cards

Rounded corners.

Soft shadows only.

Lots of breathing room.

## Buttons

Simple.

Large.

Rounded.

No flashy gradients.

## Images

Large.

High quality.

Editorial.

Often full width.